	Nonfunctional domains:

		- *.global.prod.fastly.net
		- purge.fastly.net	(times out)


	Fully covered domains:

		- *.fastly.net:

			- control
			- mirrors
			- assets1.fastly.com.a.prod	(â†’ fastly.a.ssl.fastly.net)

